name: Interspellar (Owl_Skip)
description:
A word-based puzzle game built for MashUp Game Jam 2020.

This creation had an unsually tumultuous development, built over 2 taxing days. First there were crashes, then inexplicable bugs. These proved in the end not so inexplicable but rather the result of sloppy initial programming, courtesy of yours truly. 

In the end I am pretty pleased with the results, in particular the use of some nifty HDR shaders and the computer's many hats. I hope you enjoy.

Credits

All code, art and music created by Owl_Skip in the 72 hour competition period.
